@cfbayern: Talking to Michael @Ballack today: He also has heard about the interest of @ManCity in @TimoWerner. And he is also sure: @TimoWerner will sign @ChelseaFC<br />
<img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EZ2qqH9XYAA1CAk?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEZ2qqH9XYAA1CAk%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=473d0435&s={SIZE}" /><br />
<br />
Ballack: &quot;I think it's a good decision for both sides. For Timo, because he fits there, because the way they play football suits him. I think with Chelsea, he has decided to join a club where he has a better chance of playing, which is very important to him&quot;

